title: Latin America editions of Playboy will continue to feature nude women
text:
Photo: Victor Chavez, WireImage Image 1 of / 50 50 Playboy Mexico's 2015 Playmate of the Year Elsa Day.

Photo: Victor Chavez, WireImage Image 50 of 50 Latin America editions of Playboy will continue to feature nude women 1 / 50 Back to Gallery Nude magazine enthusiasts around the world can breath a collective sigh of relief. Playboy, the gold standard of nude photo shoots, recently announced it was stepping away from being the magazine for these kinds of photo spreads, but will continue to publish women in the buff in its international editions.
RELATED: Celebrities who have posed for Playboy
Copies of Playboy produced for the Argentine and Mexican markets will continue to feature fully naked models on the cover and inside the pages it was announced this week. Teenage boys can rejoice, the nudie magazine is not dead.
